===========================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                   |NAME|EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP JOIN CARTESIAN |    |1       |5           |
|1 |├─COLUMN TABLE FULL SCAN   |A   |1       |3           |
|2 |└─MATERIAL                 |    |1       |3           |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN        |B   |1       |3           |
===========================================================
